# usejust.co deploy source

This folder (`just-app`) is the canonical source for the JUST website (usejust.co).

- All landing page, hero, and site edits belong in this project.
- `index.html` and other files here are what get committed and deployed.
- Prefer editing these files over any copy of index.html in other workspaces.
